         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Hamburg, ¶  ¶ 27 April ¶  ¶ 1853 ¶ Highly esteemed ¶  ¶ Professor!, ¶  ¶ Some time ago, Dr. F. Mueller wrote to me that it would be of ¶  ¶ use ¶  ¶ to him if he had about 20 copies of the enumeration...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">M53.04.27</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Wilhelm Sonder to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Diederich von Schlechtendal</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText" style="hyphenate: false; " xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS not seen; extracted from Tkach, Neubauer &amp; Roser (2022), Brief<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>15.</p>
                  <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
               </note>Hamburg d. 27 April 53</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Hochgeehrter Herr Professor!<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Vor einiger Zeit schrieb mir Herr Dr. F. Müller, es würde ihm von<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Nutzen</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>sein, wenn er von der Enumeratio seiner Pflanzen ungefähr 20 Exemplare zu vertheilen habe, ich möge Sie doch ersuchen, im Ganzen 25 Abdrucke anfertigen zu lassen, was er dafür zu bezahlen habe, werde er gerne entrichten. Ich entledige mich dieses Auftrages in der Hoffnung, dass es nicht zu spät sein werde. Das im März Ihnen p. Post gesandte Manuskript der Compositae <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>werden Sie erhalten haben; ich erhielt zu gleicher Zeit von Ihnen das Packet für Dr. Areschoug, welches jetzt abgeht. Die Beförderung mehrerer Kisten mit Waaren an Dr. Müller mit einem gestern expedierten Schiffe hat mich längere Zeit ganz in Anspruch genommen, auch der Besuch von Prof. Meisner und Münter hat mir einige Tage gekostet, sonst hätte ich Ihnen schon früher geschrieben, dass ich gerne bereit bin, Ihnen die Meeralgen zu bestimmen. Die in voriger Woche angekommene Sendung von Dr. Müller aus Melbourne hat wieder herrliche Sachen gebracht, 4 oder 5 neue Panax Arten, viele Moose und Farrn, Compositae, Proteaceen woraus ich eine erstaunliche Uebereinstimmung der Vegetation mit der von Van Diemensland ersehe.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Mit Hochachtung<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ihr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>ergebenster<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. Sonder<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Hamburg,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>27 April<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1853</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Highly esteemed<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Professor!,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Some time ago, Dr. F. Mueller wrote to me that it would be of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">use</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to him if he had about 20 copies of the enumeration of his plants to distribute, and that I should ask you to have 25<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>reprints made in total, for which he would be happy to pay. I<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>execute<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>this task in the hope that it will not be too late. You will have received the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>manuscript of the Compositae<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>sent to you by post in March; at the same time I received from you the package for Dr.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Areschoug, which now goes off. The<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>dispatch<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>several boxes of goods to Dr. Mueller on a ship that was<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>sent off<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>yesterday has taken me a long time. The<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>visit of Prof. Meisner and Münter has also<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>cost<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>me a few days, otherwise I would have written<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to you earlier that I am gladly prepared<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to determine the seaweeds<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>for you.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>The shipment of Dr. Mueller from Melbourne, which arrived last week, has again brought wonderful things, 4 or 5 new<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Panax</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>species, many mosses and ferns, Compositae,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Proteaceae,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>from which I see an astonishing<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>agreement of the vegetation with<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that of Van Diemen's<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Land.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">With Respect</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>most devoted</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">W. Sonder</seg>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
